description: Try our easy to follow Banana Bread recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Banana Bread Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Spoon into prepared pan and smooth top. Bake for 1 hour or until cooked when tested with a skewer. Stand for 5 minutes before transferring to a wire rack to cool. Slice and serve.
